Post Installation
================


On Gnome 2.24 or newer
----------------------
1. Add the applet (GlobalMenu PanelApplet) to the panel.
2. Enable the Gtk Plugin from the preference window of the applet.

On Gnome 2.22 or older
----------------------

1. Edit your .bash_profile, add

{{{
export GTK_MODULES=globalmenu-gnome
}}}

2. Add the applet (GlobalMenu PanelApplet) to the panel.
